This paper deals with the task of attribute transfer in images, specifically in facial images. This task falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) domain. The paper proposes a novel method using generative adversarial networks (GANs), which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves inpainting, which is a technique used in graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) domains. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, and cs.MM.
